imdb.plot outline: Lakestesterdam follows the trials and tribulations of the two charismatic owners of the Evergreen Holistic, based in the collective they dub Lakesterdam. The pair struggle to keep the doors open in the completive collective they call Lakesterdam. The deal with the looming threat of legalization, a bevy of challenging patients and employees alike to keep the doors open.
